		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Hey everyone
<br />
<br />I would like to know if I could get a 64 bit of NESASM and other development stuff... I tried some versions but they wouldn't work in 64 bit.
<br />
<br />Also, best place to get started on developing an NES game? Like, a tutorial or a guide how to develop a game; which programs to use etc.
<br />
<br />Thank you very much in advance =)
<br />
<br />(Also, can I use .NSF files made in famitracker for the games?)

		

